#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn23.13"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn23.13:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 23 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 23 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.13:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyamāravagga "
msgstr "2. About Māra (2nd) "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 13. Aniccasutta → anicca 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn23.13:0.3"
msgid "13. Aniccasutta "
msgstr "13. Impermanence "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn23.13:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.13:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā rādho bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Seated to one side, Venerable Rādha said to the Buddha: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.13:1.3"
msgid "“‘aniccaṃ, aniccan’ti, bhante, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of this thing called ‘impermanence’. "

msgctxt "sn23.13:1.4"
msgid "Katamaṃ nu kho, bhante, aniccan”ti? "
msgstr "What is impermanence?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.13:1.5"
msgid "“Rūpaṃ kho, rādha, aniccaṃ, vedanā aniccā, saññā aniccā, saṅkhārā aniccā, viññāṇaṃ aniccaṃ. "
msgstr "“Rādha, form, feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness are impermanent. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.13:1.6"
msgid "Evaṃ passaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "Seeing this … "

msgctxt "sn23.13:1.7"
msgid "nāparaṃ itthattāyāti pajānātī”ti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘… there is no return to any state of existence.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn23.13:1.8"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
